
This directory contains source code for the ARPS 
3D variational Data Analysis System. 

run the 3dvar:

  makearps 3dvar
  bin/3dvar<input/arp.input.f90
 
3dvar.f90: preparing observation data for the
analysis. 

Gminimization.f90  Minimization driver.

Gcostf3d.f90       Calculating the cost function.

Ggradc3d.f90       Calculating the gradient of cost function.

Gminim_sub.f90     Limited Memory Gonjuagate gradient method.


